section_summary: The text appears to be a transcript or record of a meeting or session. It includes discussions about nominations and appointments for various committees, specifically the Committee on Internal Affairs and Defense. The names of individuals who have been nominated for this committee are mentioned, including Khaled Al-Ateeby, Khaled Al-Tammar, Majed Al-Mutairi, Badr Al-Shammari, and Dr. Mohammed Al-Mahan. The text also mentions the general secretary of the National Assembly and the management of sessions. The date of the text is June 20, 2023.
